Documentation
Project Title

AI SEO Blog & Content Cluster Generator

Business Chosen

Shyam Institute, Kakinada

Tool Used

ChatGPT (OpenAI)

Project Overview

The AI SEO Blog & Content Cluster Generator is a Prompt Engineering project that uses Artificial Intelligence to create SEO-focused content for local businesses.

This project generates:

Primary Keywords
Secondary Keywords
Search Intent
SEO Meta Title
SEO Meta Description
Pillar Blog Content
Supporting Blog Topics
Internal Linking Suggestions
Local SEO Recommendations

The objective is to help businesses improve their online visibility, attract relevant website visitors, and rank higher on search engines such as Google.

Prompt Used
You are an SEO Content Strategist.

Business Name: Shyam Institute
Business Type: Coaching Institute
Location: Kakinada

Generate:

1. Primary Keyword
2. Secondary Keywords
3. Search Intent
4. SEO Meta Title
5. SEO Meta Description
6. Pillar Blog Outline (H1-H3)
7. 1200+ Word Pillar Blog
8. 5 Supporting Blog Topics
9. Internal Linking Suggestions
10. Local SEO Recommendations

Tone:
Professional
Informative
SEO-Friendly
Local Business Focused
Prompt Logic

The prompt follows a structured SEO content generation framework.

Input
Business Name
Business Type
Location
AI Processing

The AI analyzes the business information and generates:

Relevant keywords
Search intent
SEO metadata
Long-form pillar content
Content cluster ideas
Local SEO recommendations
Output

A complete SEO content strategy that can be used for:

Website Blogs
Google Rankings
Content Marketing
Local SEO Campaigns
